{"title":"南极行","authors":["金乃千"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南极行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金乃千"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒流送君南极去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风望君北国还"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知冰源秋未到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏日低回一百天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皑皑银装披古原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泱泱碧海白玉磐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船到冰缘疑无路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹水暖入极圈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天高夏日低"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰山映涟漪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"极地无夜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳共晨曦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君留东海地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我自南极去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥遥三万里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两情长依依"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里重洋万缕思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男儿奋战好梦痴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待到中山崛起日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南极北地两相知"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"津门赤子涌海情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半百之躯越西风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬冰卧雪南极地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白髯童心入银屏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男儿有志踏荆途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰原雪岭建巨屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南极地上红一角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤子群中才人出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飒爽男儿跃海出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文武刚柔气不俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫道细小无大义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足迹斑斑写宏图"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老来豪气壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别家越重洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不畏西风恶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所懼冰崩狂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足踏南极地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗洒丘陵岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中山伴日起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白雪映红妆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年过半百心似童"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨海南行沐西风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏遍冰山人未老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抒尽南极赤子情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以上十首为１９８９年元月至３月所咏记此。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者附记："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金乃千同志是中央戏剧学院副教授、著名话剧演员。１９８８年底，为拍摄电视剧《长城向南延伸》，毅然南下登上极地，表现了一个无产阶级文艺战士崇高的精神和胆识，归国途中重病，不幸以身殉职。本报特发表他在南极时写下的１０首诗，以志怀念。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}